Richard L. Greenberg, CFA, Senior Vice President
				Senior Portfolio Manager/Director of Research

With the firm over 33 years, Mr. Greenberg began his investment industry career at Home Insurance Co. as an industry analyst, focusing primarily on the metals, banking and housing sectors. Mr. Greenberg graduated Phi Beta Kappa from SUNY (Binghamton) with a B.A. in psychology, and received his MBA from Wharton Business School.

	 
 




















