John Piermont, CFA
				Research Analyst

With the company since 2010.  Mr. Piermont was a Vice President at Citi Institutional Consulting, a division of Smith Barney that he co-founded in 2005. Prior to CIC, he was an Assistant Vice President in the Smith Barney Strategy and Finance Group. Mr. Piermont received a B.A. in Economics from Dartmouth College and an MBA from Columbia Business School where he was a member of the value investing program.

	 
 




















