            Established in 1975 as Home Portfolio Advisors Inc., Donald Smith & Co. Inc. is an employee-owned firm, which received its present name in 1983. It is a registered investment adviser of value investing that specializes in managing equity accounts for large tax-exempt and taxable funds. Located in New York City, Donald Smith & Co. Inc. offers five products, including All Cap Value, Large Cap Concentrated Value, Midcap Value, Small Cap Value and Micro Cap Value equities.
          






















